data.description: Beautiful move-in ready 3 bedroom home with 2 1/2 bathrooms in highly desired Redbird Ranch Community! Large living areas throughout the home with custom Luxury Vinyl Plank and ceramic tile flooring. Open living room leads into first dining area; kitchen offers stainless steel appliances with dark cabinets & a second eating area.  Spacious Master bedroom includes a full bathroom with double sink vanity, shower with separate garden tub and a spacious walk in closet.  Private fenced in backyard is perfect for gathering and entertaining. This property is available to be purchased fully furnished for an additional fee, providing you with a seamless transition into your new lifestyle!
